<title>yswʿ fdạny</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- yswʿ fdạny bdmh ʿly̱ ạlṣlyb
 wbḥbh rwạny bạlḥrbẗ wạlmsạmyr
 ạ̉nạ rạyḥ wạ̉nạ wạtẖq llsmạ ʿn qryb
 ạ̹lhy hyạkẖdny dh ḥbyby msẖ bʿyd
 yswʿy yswʿy yswʿy fdạny
 2- fy kẖyrh ạ̉nạ ʿạysẖ ʿly̱ ṭwl sẖạyl hmy
 dh slạmy fy nhạry wạllyl byḥrsny
 msẖ kẖạyf wạ̉nạ mạsẖy lwḥdy fy ạlṭryq
 dh ḥạmyny wḍmạny yswʿy ạ̉ḥly̱ ṣdyq
 yswʿy yswʿy yswʿy ṣdyqẗ</lyrics>
</song>